Description: Unified decentralized platform for the Grain Network
 Grainspace is a comprehensive decentralized platform that integrates:
  - ICP (Internet Computer Protocol) canisters
  - Nostr decentralized social protocol
  - Urbit personal server network
  - Grainspace Network identity management
 .
 It provides a unified interface for managing decentralized applications,
 photos, writing, and development workflows across the Grain Hardware
 Ecosystem (Graincamera, Grainwriter, Grainpack).
 .
 Features:
  - Self-hosted AI development with Qwen3, Gemini, Llama, GPT-OS
  - Native AVIF photo management
  - E-ink writing device integration
  - External GPU acceleration support
  - Decentralized identity via Urbit Azimuth
  - Multi-chain payment support (ICP + Solana)


